<br>
We should all be very proud of this raid, as we are on a winning streak of 3 straight dragons! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  We OWNED Vox! I've got some good ideas to speed up the raid for next time. Once again, thanks to all those who came and gave their all! <br>
