<br>
Once I was at around 50 mana, and nothing landing, I decided to run out to the healing line and started dropping mod rods. It was near the end of the battle though, so I dont know how much use that actually was. My pet lasted until the end though, so he at least was doing damage. Go pet.<br>
<br>
