<br>
One question on the bears, are they conisdered animals? Are there usually icy terrors in the bear pits? Im curious, because I realized after the fact (again, smart me) that I had my earthen boots on, which when activated, produce a nice, instant cast invis vs. animals. If they are infact considered animals, Mages would do well to hotkey their boots if they have them, and hit it the instant they find themselves falling through.<br>
